{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Firefox 3 Dom Improvements","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/3/DOM_improvements","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"\n  <ol>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n        <details>\n            <summary>Firefox developer release notes</summary>\n            <ol>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases\">Firefox developer release notes</a></li>\n            </ol>\n        </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n        <details>\n            <summary>擴充套件</summary>\n            <ol>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/Add-ons/WebExtensions\">瀏覽器擴充功能</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/Add-ons/Themes\">主題</a></li>\n            </ol>\n        </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n        <details>\n            <summary>Firefox internals</summary>\n            <ol>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/\">Mozilla project</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/Gecko\">Gecko</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Headless_mode\">Headless mode</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/JavaScript_code_modules\">JavaScript 程式碼模組</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/js-ctypes\">JS-ctypes</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/MathML_Project\">MathML 專案</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/MFBT\">MFBT</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/Projects\">Mozilla 專案</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/Preferences\">Preference system</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/WebIDL_bindings\">WebIDL bindings</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/Tech/XPCOM\">XPCOM</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/Tech/XUL\">XUL</a></li>\n            </ol>\n        </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n        <details>\n            <summary>Building and contributing</summary>\n            <ol>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/Developer_guide/Build_Instructions\">建置教學</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/Developer_guide/Build_Instructions/Configuring_Build_Options\">Configuring build options</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/Developer_guide/Build_Instructions/How_Mozilla_s_build_system_works\">How the build system works</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/Developer_guide/Source_Code/Mercurial\">Mozilla 原始碼</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/Localization\">在地化</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/Mercurial\">Mercurial</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/QA\">Quality assurance</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/Using_Mozilla_code_in_other_projects\">在我們的專案中使用 Mozilla 程式碼</a></li>\n            </ol>\n        </details>\n    </li>\n  </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"firefox_3_對_dom_的改善","title":"Firefox 3 對 DOM 的改善","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Firefox 3 對 DOM 做了一些改善，改善重點之一就是加強對於「其他瀏覽器對 DOM 所增加的延伸規格」的支援。</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>支援 IE 的延伸規格 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/DOM:element.clientTop\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">clientTop</a> 與 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/DOM:element.clientLeft\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">clientLeft</a>。</li>\n  <li>現在不論在哪裡讀取，<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/fullScreen\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">wondow.fullScreen (en-US)</a> perperty 可以總是保持正確，即使在 content 內也一樣。先前會錯誤地回報 false (<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=127013\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug127013</a>) 。</li>\n  <li>支援 IE 的延伸規格 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/getClientRects\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">getClientRects (en-US)</a> and <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/getBoundingClientRect\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">getBoundingClientRect (en-US)</a> (<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=174397\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug 174397</a>).</li>\n  <li>支援 IE 的延伸規格 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/elementFromPoint\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">elementFromPoint (en-US)</a> (<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=199692\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug 199692</a>)</li>\n  <li>支援 IE 的延伸規格 oncut, oncopy, onpaste, onbeforecut, onbeforecopy and onbeforepaste (<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=280959\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug 280959</a>)</li>\n  <li>新增可以用於 Node.nodePrincipal, Node.baseURIObject, and <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/DOM:document.documentURIObject\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">document.documentURIObject</a> 的 privileged-code-only getters。Chrome code 絕對不可以在 unwrapped content object (例如： 在 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/XPCNativeWrapper\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">XPCNativeWrapper</a> 的 wrappedJSObject) 上 touch (get or set) 這些 properties，詳見 <a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=324464\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug 324464</a>。</li>\n  <li>支援 The Web Applications 1.0 (HTML5) 的 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/getElementsByClassName\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">getElementsByClassName() (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"參考資料","title":"參考資料","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/3/DOM_improvements\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">DOM Improvements in Firefox 3 原始網頁 (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"延伸閱讀","title":"延伸閱讀","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/3\">Firefox 3 開發人員須知</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Firefox_3_CSS_Improvement\">Firefox 3 對 CSS 的改善</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document_Object_Model\">DOM</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Firefox 3 對 DOM 做了一些改善，改善重點之一就是加強對於「其他瀏覽器對 DOM 所增加的延伸規格」的支援。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"DOM improvements in Firefox 3","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Mejoras DOM en Firefox 3","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Améliorations DOM dans Firefox 3","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Firefox 3 での DOM の改良","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/mozilla/firefox/releases/3/dom_improvements","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/mozilla/firefox/releases/3/dom_improvements/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla","title":"Mozilla"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/Firefox","title":"Firefox"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases","title":"Firefox 各版本技術文件"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/3","title":"Firefox 3 技術文件"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/3/DOM_improvements","title":"Firefox 3 Dom Improvements"}],"pageTitle":"Firefox 3 Dom Improvements - Mozilla | MDN","noIndexing":false}}